<h3>Question 9</h3>
<div><p><p>Use Mann-Whitney U test to assess whether the following satisfaction score based on the performance of two different special types of gadgets at 5% level of significance.</p>
<div class="table_wrapper"><table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Gadget A</td>
<td>   50</td>
<td>    40</td>
<td>    30</td>
<td>    20</td>
